name: Aerodrome Reinvest
description: Supplies {{token}} to [Aerodrome Finance](https://aerodrome.finance/liquidity) and stakes it in the gauge to collect any available tokens and earn AERO rewards. Rewards are harvested, sold for more {{token}}, and deposited back into the strategy.
